[{"Code":"en","Title":"Customize checkout page","Slug":"customize-checkout-page","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"88eceaf5-db67-4c42-8176-5ac7bb1053d1\">The Xendit-hosted checkout page supports customization to make it more personalized for your business. You can easily set this up through the Xendit Dashboard.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"6959cfd2-9a24-40d9-8fb9-e1cf61a3cd98\"><strong>Customize appearance</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"1468d710-b573-4095-9c57-ef6f0ba321ca\">You can adjust the appearance of the hosted page to match your business's branding by customizing the colors. Navigate to: <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#customize-appearance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; Checkout &gt; Customize Appearance.</strong></a></p><p data-block-id=\"0fb7b5c6-2bd5-42ce-a3f4-d8084f1b4653\">The changes will automatically apply to all Payment Links created, ensuring a consistent and branded customer experience.</p><p data-block-id=\"1f0c1f6e-e2f8-4dad-9a50-c40dba9af75e\"><img data-block-id=\"833a721e-5529-4ee1-b74b-bfb7769a9660\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(91).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(91).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"764\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:764px;width:764px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:382px;\"><col style=\"width:382px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"06794755-e9ab-43e8-bc30-29395630a410\"><strong>Setting</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"57250b87-e543-4caa-ab72-161f400b96fc\"><strong>Details</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"686faeec-a766-4a17-b6a4-a3595ea5262c\"><strong>Preview</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4f00f6db-7da3-4d71-ac43-33a61e01dc93\">See how the UI looks on different devices (desktop and mobile).</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"c4283925-88d8-4512-b7e3-6ad6bfb56f2e\"><strong>Background Color</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"05f54067-948b-4943-9580-f8bc1d2c718e\">Choose an RGB color that reflects your brand's identity.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"3f8f6902-aef7-4521-aace-94c0e193f1c2\"><strong>Buttons &amp; Accents</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4d037a37-cdcd-4f76-b357-ff342d37799d\">Adjust button colors and other accent elements to enhance the aesthetic of the checkout.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"e6987591-ec05-4112-bd2c-75eb4c04c4ef\"><strong>Time Format</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"696bbe28-72e6-4e42-918b-d0771a8ff8d0\">Select between 12-hour or 24-hour formats for time display.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"3e78e151-235e-4c21-aab3-40adcb828a38\"><strong>Payment settings</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"3cc7cec5-4822-4a59-ad09-1ff802b4881c\">You can customize the Xendit-hosted page at the payment settings level. This allows you to:</p><ul data-block-id=\"eecfca64-eadd-4dbc-b832-62e5e7df4c27\"><li data-block-id=\"64e9635a-fb42-43cd-903e-2e5d96deeb5a\"><p data-block-id=\"cac8c890-d5b6-49a5-985b-81d8ea83505d\">Choose which payment channels to display</p></li><li data-block-id=\"faa4ca97-30d3-40d9-8d70-315529289f70\"><p data-block-id=\"1578ba5f-db95-4fe8-9006-cd7d3db37e0b\">Set the default language and currency</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fab660ad-5a1d-4a35-987c-daffd0316901\"><p data-block-id=\"fa379dec-695b-4b71-8e81-447556395575\">Define the default duration for payment links</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f5c795cb-7078-4e00-bbca-bcc8eb2c4fe5\">To configure these settings, go to <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#payment-settings\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; Checkout &gt; Payment Settings</strong></a>. Once set, these preferences will apply to all Payment Links <em>unless specific settings are defined during their creation.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"0e874c08-9f07-491a-97cb-8d3c34574e23\"><img data-block-id=\"5bffcb19-6a2b-447a-b930-a6cdc59020d2\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(92).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(92).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Customize checkout page","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Halaman checkout kustom","Slug":"customize-xendit-hosted-page","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcbomq3y-gpl54o-306\">Halaman checkout yang dihosting Xendit mendukung penyesuaian agar lebih dipersonalisasi untuk bisnis Anda. Anda dapat dengan mudah mengaturnya melalui Dasbor Xendit.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"mcbomq40-4x5j6i-307\"><strong>Sesuaikan tampilan</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq40-juiwt7-308\">Anda dapat menyesuaikan tampilan halaman yang dihosting agar sesuai dengan branding bisnis Anda dengan menyesuaikan warna. Untuk melakukan ini, buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#customize-appearance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Dasbor Xendit &gt; Pengaturan &gt; Pembayaran &gt; Kustomisasi Tampilan</strong></a>.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq40-6x0lbg-309\">Perubahan akan secara otomatis berlaku untuk semua Link Pembayaran yang dibuat, memastikan pengalaman pelanggan yang konsisten.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq40-psl7cq-310\"><img data-block-id=\"mcbomq40-k0qwjj-311\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(91).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(91).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"764\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:764px;width:764px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:382px;\"><col style=\"width:382px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq41-5z2cc2-312\"><strong>Pengaturan</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq41-53awgu-313\"><strong>Rincian</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq41-lra6nv-314\"><strong>Preview</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq42-x5thi7-315\">Lihat tampilan UI di berbagai perangkat (desktop dan seluler).</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq42-4r6sal-316\"><strong>Warna Latar Belakang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq42-glulua-317\">Pilih warna RGB yang mencerminkan identitas merek Anda.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq42-snrohk-318\"><strong>Tombol &amp; Aksen</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-abfebf-319\">Sesuaikan warna tombol dan elemen aksen lainnya untuk meningkatkan estetika checkout.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-0k0pkb-320\"><strong>Format Waktu</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-4f18j5-321\">Pilih antara format 12 jam atau 24 jam untuk tampilan waktu.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-mf6hs4-322\"><strong>Pengaturan pembayaran</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-s997lw-323\">Anda dapat menyesuaikan halaman yang dihosting Xendit di tingkat pengaturan pembayaran. Ini memungkinkan Anda untuk:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-vp2c9p-324\"><li data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-atuexb-325\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-lnx8h8-326\">Pilih channel pembayaran yang akan ditampilkan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-iy8dwi-327\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-1hhala-328\">Atur bahasa dan mata uang default</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-mc1hwk-329\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-akot8l-330\">Tentukan durasi default untuk link pembayaran</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq43-nqoy86-331\">Untuk mengonfigurasi pengaturan ini, buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#payment-settings\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Dasbor Xendit &gt; Pengaturan &gt; Checkout &gt; Pengaturan Pembayaran</strong></a>. Setelah ditetapkan, preferensi ini akan berlaku untuk semua link Pembayaran <em>kecuali pengaturan khusus ditentukan selama pembuatannya.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mcbomq44-i87rop-332\"><img data-block-id=\"mcbomq44-qiigjz-333\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(92).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(92).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Halaman checkout kustom","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ปรับแต่งหน้าชำระเงิน","Slug":"customize-xendit-hosted-page","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"88eceaf5-db67-4c42-8176-5ac7bb1053d1\">หน้าชำระเงินที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit รองรับการปรับแต่งเพื่อให้เป็นส่วนตัวสำหรับธุรกิจของคุณมากขึ้น คุณสามารถตั้งค่านี้ได้อย่างง่ายดายผ่าน Xendit Dashboard</p><h3 data-block-id=\"6959cfd2-9a24-40d9-8fb9-e1cf61a3cd98\"><strong>ปรับแต่งรูปลักษณ์</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"1468d710-b573-4095-9c57-ef6f0ba321ca\">คุณสามารถปรับรูปลักษณ์ของหน้าเพจที่โฮสต์ให้เข้ากับแบรนด์ของธุรกิจคุณได้โดยการปรับแต่งสี ไปที่: <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#customize-appearance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; Checkout &gt; Customize Appearance.</strong></a></p><p data-block-id=\"0fb7b5c6-2bd5-42ce-a3f4-d8084f1b4653\">การเปลี่ยนแปลงจะถูกนำไปใช้โดยอัตโนมัติกับ Payment Links ทั้งหมดที่สร้างขึ้น เพื่อให้มั่นใจว่าลูกค้าจะได้รับประสบการณ์ที่สอดคล้องและเป็นไปตามแบรนด์</p><p data-block-id=\"1f0c1f6e-e2f8-4dad-9a50-c40dba9af75e\"><img data-block-id=\"833a721e-5529-4ee1-b74b-bfb7769a9660\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(91).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(91).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"764\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:764px;width:764px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:382px;\"><col style=\"width:382px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"06794755-e9ab-43e8-bc30-29395630a410\"><strong>การตั้งค่า</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"57250b87-e543-4caa-ab72-161f400b96fc\"><strong>รายละเอียด</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"686faeec-a766-4a17-b6a4-a3595ea5262c\"><strong>ตัวอย่าง (Preview)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4f00f6db-7da3-4d71-ac43-33a61e01dc93\">ดูว่า UI มีลักษณะอย่างไรบนอุปกรณ์ต่างๆ (เดสก์ท็อปและมือถือ)</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"c4283925-88d8-4512-b7e3-6ad6bfb56f2e\"><strong>สีพื้นหลัง (Background Color)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"05f54067-948b-4943-9580-f8bc1d2c718e\">เลือกสี RGB ที่สะท้อนถึงเอกลักษณ์ของแบรนด์คุณ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"3f8f6902-aef7-4521-aace-94c0e193f1c2\"><strong>ปุ่มและองค์ประกอบเน้น (Buttons &amp; Accents)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4d037a37-cdcd-4f76-b357-ff342d37799d\">ปรับสีปุ่มและองค์ประกอบเน้นอื่นๆ เพื่อเพิ่มความสวยงามของหน้าชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"e6987591-ec05-4112-bd2c-75eb4c04c4ef\"><strong>รูปแบบเวลา (Time Format)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"696bbe28-72e6-4e42-918b-d0771a8ff8d0\">เลือกระหว่างรูปแบบ 12 ชั่วโมงหรือ 24 ชั่วโมงสำหรับการแสดงเวลา</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"3e78e151-235e-4c21-aab3-40adcb828a38\"><strong>การตั้งค่าการชำระเงิน</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"3cc7cec5-4822-4a59-ad09-1ff802b4881c\">คุณสามารถปรับแต่งหน้าเพจที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit ในระดับการตั้งค่าการชำระเงิน ซึ่งช่วยให้คุณสามารถ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"eecfca64-eadd-4dbc-b832-62e5e7df4c27\"><li data-block-id=\"64e9635a-fb42-43cd-903e-2e5d96deeb5a\"><p data-block-id=\"cac8c890-d5b6-49a5-985b-81d8ea83505d\">เลือกช่องทางการชำระเงินที่จะแสดง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"faa4ca97-30d3-40d9-8d70-315529289f70\"><p data-block-id=\"1578ba5f-db95-4fe8-9006-cd7d3db37e0b\">กำหนดภาษาและสกุลเงินเริ่มต้น</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fab660ad-5a1d-4a35-987c-daffd0316901\"><p data-block-id=\"fa379dec-695b-4b71-8e81-447556395575\">กำหนดระยะเวลาเริ่มต้นสำหรับ Payment Links</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f5c795cb-7078-4e00-bbca-bcc8eb2c4fe5\">หากต้องการกำหนดค่าการตั้งค่าเหล่านี้ ไปที่ <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#payment-settings\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; Checkout &gt; Payment Settings</strong></a> เมื่อตั้งค่าแล้ว การตั้งค่าเหล่านี้จะถูกนำไปใช้กับ Payment Links ทั้งหมด <em>เว้นแต่จะมีการกำหนดการตั้งค่าเฉพาะเจาะจงในระหว่างการสร้าง Payment Links นั้นๆ</em></p><p data-block-id=\"0e874c08-9f07-491a-97cb-8d3c34574e23\"><img data-block-id=\"5bffcb19-6a2b-447a-b930-a6cdc59020d2\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(92).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(92).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ปรับแต่งหน้าชำระเงิน","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Personalizar página de pago","Slug":"customize-checkout-page","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"88eceaf5-db67-4c42-8176-5ac7bb1053d1\">La página de pago alojada por Xendit admite personalización para hacerla más personalizada para su negocio. Usted puede configurarla fácilmente a través del Xendit Dashboard.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"6959cfd2-9a24-40d9-8fb9-e1cf61a3cd98\"><strong>Personalizar apariencia</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"1468d710-b573-4095-9c57-ef6f0ba321ca\">Usted puede ajustar la apariencia de la página alojada para que coincida con la marca de su negocio personalizando los colores. Navegue a: <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#customize-appearance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Configuración &gt; Checkout &gt; Customize Appearance.</strong></a></p><p data-block-id=\"0fb7b5c6-2bd5-42ce-a3f4-d8084f1b4653\">Los cambios se aplicarán automáticamente a todos los Payment Links creados, asegurando una experiencia de cliente consistente y de marca.</p><p data-block-id=\"1f0c1f6e-e2f8-4dad-9a50-c40dba9af75e\"><img data-block-id=\"833a721e-5529-4ee1-b74b-bfb7769a9660\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(91).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(91).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"764\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:764px;width:764px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:382px;\"><col style=\"width:382px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"06794755-e9ab-43e8-bc30-29395630a410\"><strong>Configuración</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"57250b87-e543-4caa-ab72-161f400b96fc\"><strong>Detalles</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"686faeec-a766-4a17-b6a4-a3595ea5262c\"><strong>Vista previa</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4f00f6db-7da3-4d71-ac43-33a61e01dc93\">Vea cómo se ve la UI en diferentes dispositivos (escritorio y móvil).</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"c4283925-88d8-4512-b7e3-6ad6bfb56f2e\"><strong>Color de fondo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"05f54067-948b-4943-9580-f8bc1d2c718e\">Elija un color RGB que refleje la identidad de su marca.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"3f8f6902-aef7-4521-aace-94c0e193f1c2\"><strong>Botones y acentos</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"4d037a37-cdcd-4f76-b357-ff342d37799d\">Ajuste los colores de los botones y otros elementos de acento para mejorar la estética del checkout.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"e6987591-ec05-4112-bd2c-75eb4c04c4ef\"><strong>Formato de hora</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"382\"><p data-block-id=\"696bbe28-72e6-4e42-918b-d0771a8ff8d0\">Seleccione entre formatos de 12 horas o 24 horas para la visualización de la hora.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"3e78e151-235e-4c21-aab3-40adcb828a38\"><strong>Configuración de pago</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"3cc7cec5-4822-4a59-ad09-1ff802b4881c\">Usted puede personalizar la página alojada por Xendit a nivel de configuración de pago. Esto le permite:</p><ul data-block-id=\"eecfca64-eadd-4dbc-b832-62e5e7df4c27\"><li data-block-id=\"64e9635a-fb42-43cd-903e-2e5d96deeb5a\"><p data-block-id=\"cac8c890-d5b6-49a5-985b-81d8ea83505d\">Elegir qué canales de pago mostrar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"faa4ca97-30d3-40d9-8d70-315529289f70\"><p data-block-id=\"1578ba5f-db95-4fe8-9006-cd7d3db37e0b\">Establecer el idioma y la moneda predeterminados</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fab660ad-5a1d-4a35-987c-daffd0316901\"><p data-block-id=\"fa379dec-695b-4b71-8e81-447556395575\">Definir la duración predeterminada para los Payment Links</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f5c795cb-7078-4e00-bbca-bcc8eb2c4fe5\">Para configurar estos ajustes, vaya a <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/checkout#payment-settings\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Dashboard &gt; Configuración &gt; Checkout &gt; Payment Settings</strong></a>. Una vez establecidas, estas preferencias se aplicarán a todos los Payment Links <em>a menos que se definan configuraciones específicas durante su creación.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"0e874c08-9f07-491a-97cb-8d3c34574e23\"><img data-block-id=\"5bffcb19-6a2b-447a-b930-a6cdc59020d2\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(92).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(92).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Personalizar página de pago","Description":null}]